            "title": "聲稱銀行服務遭剝奪 特朗普將摩通和戴蒙告上法庭索賠50億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"聲稱銀行服務遭剝奪 特朗普將摩通和戴蒙告上法庭索賠50億美元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7MkOdJpDY4dZEI5au.uPsQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/9fac7010-f7a8-11f0-bcd7-f35b65ae1f00\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聲稱銀行服務遭剝奪 特朗普將摩通和戴蒙告上法庭索賠50億美元</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
