        {
            "title": "蘋果擴大硬體主管Ternus職權 釋放CEO接班人信號",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Source: Getty Images North America\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"634\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OTpkdWOlvvydVbAIhw5JYw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/06274aa7883b2d33753dd169b46643f6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Source: Getty Images North America</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 蘋果公司將設計工作納入硬體主管John Ternus的職責範圍，鞏固了他作為未來接任執行長蒂姆·庫克的熱門人選地位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，自2011年起領導蘋果公司並在去年11月年滿65歲的庫克，在去年年底悄然任命Ternus負責管理公司的設計團隊。此舉擴大了Ternus的職責範圍，使他接手了公司最關鍵職能之一。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"John TernusSource: Getty Images North America\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"634\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pgSDjB2ea_lsG8zpEUrXlQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7464c318e83b7e23460a031b1882a733\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">John TernusSource: Getty Images North America</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些職責在蘋果公司具有特殊意義。這個涵蓋對硬體和軟件設計管理的職位長期以來由資深領導者出任。自喬布斯時代以來，蘋果的成功始終與其產品的外觀和使用體驗密切相關。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-14ace0cf-837a-3d3c-8d69-ef670101033d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：庫克的CEO帥印 或交給蘋果土生土長的自己人</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘋果公司發言人拒絕發表評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Apple Expands Hardware Chief’s Role in Signal of CEO Candidacy</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%A1%AC%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1ternus%E8%81%B7%E6%AC%8A-%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BEceo%E6%8E%A5%E7%8F%AD%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F-193522406.html",
