        {
            "title": "金融時報：馬斯克SpaceX公司擬聘美銀、高盛等四大行牽頭IPO",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據英國《金融時報》報導，馬斯克的火箭與衛星公司SpaceX已選定四家銀行擔任首次公開募股的牽頭行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導引述知情人士消息稱，SpaceX計畫讓美國銀行、高盛集團、摩根大通和摩根士丹利擔任高級承銷角色。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據熟悉籌備工作的知情人士透露，SpaceX計畫最早今年進行IPO，融資額將遠超300億美元，該交易對公司的估值約為1.5萬億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博新聞12月報導，該公司目前正推進一項內部股票出售，該交易對公司估值約為8000億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-637eaf73-c63e-3590-a087-756d4eebec7a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《金融時報》指出，其他銀行也可能參與SpaceX的IPO，目前尚未做出最終決定。上述銀行均拒絕向《金融時報》置評，而SpaceX也暫未回應。SpaceX 的代表未回覆彭博置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SpaceX在12月告知員工，公司正進入「靜默期」，要求員工避免討論IPO事宜。這是擬上市公司在預期首次亮相前幾個月必須遵守的監管要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Musk’s SpaceX Lines Up Banks to Lead IPO, Financial Times Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8Bspacex%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%93%AC%E8%81%98%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%89%BD%E9%A0%ADipo-165030736.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 01:41:05",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "烏克蘭總統澤連斯基會晤川普後指責歐洲盟友流於空談",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 俄烏戰爭進入第四年之際，烏克蘭在俄羅斯的頻繁轟炸下陷入斷水、斷暖、斷電困境。該國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:澤連斯基;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澤連斯基\">澤連斯基</a>在達沃斯指責歐洲缺乏阻止普丁的意願。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周四的演講中，澤連斯基稱歐洲盟友既不能攔截俄羅斯的「影子艦隊」油輪，對沒收凍結的俄羅斯資產也是縮手縮腳，在美國注意力轉向他處時，歐洲缺乏作為真正全球大國採取行動的意志。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「歐洲喜歡討論未來，卻回避在當下採取行動，」一臉憤怒的澤連斯基對台下聽眾說。「那些準備採取行動的領導人都在哪兒？」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e52d104f-ff65-3910-9c38-813a4856c804-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位烏克蘭總統在發表講話前，匆忙趕往達沃斯與川普舉行了一場臨時安排的會晤。川普形容這次會晤是「良好的」，並再次表達了對俄烏戰爭儘早結束的期待。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基在演講中稱，「我們不應接受歐洲只是一個由中小國家拼湊而成、還夾雜著歐洲敵人的‘沙拉’。當烏克蘭與你們並肩時，沒有人敢踐踏你們，你們將永遠擁有採取行動的途徑，而且是及時的行動。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Zelenskiy Slams Europe for Inaction in Countering Putin</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%BE%8C%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%8B%E6%B5%81%E6%96%BC%E7%A9%BA%E8%AB%87-145959177.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 23:34:59",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國首次申請失業救濟人數穩定在20萬 顯示裁員規模有限",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國上周首次申領失業救濟人數基本持平，在假日季波動過後維持在低位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國勞工部周四公佈的數據顯示，截至1月17日當周，首次申領失業救濟人數增加1,000人，至20萬人。彭博對經濟學家的調查顯示，預估中值為20.9萬人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去三年中，首次申領失業救濟人數達到或低於20萬人的情況並不多見，其中大多出現在假日前後。此類水平與裁員規模有限的勞動力市場特徵相符。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在連續三次降息以提振就業市場之後，市場普遍預計，聯儲會官員將在下周召開的今年首次政策會議上維持利率不變。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6c298210-16c9-3c91-81c9-7a761780946d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">四周移動均值上周降至201,500人，創兩年低點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">持續申領失業救濟人數在此前一周降至185萬人，創11月份以來最低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Jobless Claims Steady at 200,000 in Sign of Low Layoffs (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%91%E6%BF%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%A820%E8%90%AC-%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90-140049570.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 22:49:44",
